  "detailed_description": "<h1>Featured DLC</h1><p></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><strong>WATCHERS</strong> is a free-to-play Battle Royale top-down shooter where killed battlers remain in play thanks to the game's unique Watcher game mode. <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1124980/extras/271478a292cf2801daf4ad3dc6302f95.poster.avif?t=1625073737\" width=500 height=374 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1124980/extras/271478a292cf2801daf4ad3dc6302f95.webm?t=1625073737\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1124980/extras/271478a292cf2801daf4ad3dc6302f95.mp4?t=1625073737\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>BATTLER</strong> mode:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> 24-player top-down Battle Royale action.<br></li><li> An unpredictable outcome: the fewer battlers survive, the more Watchers there are to plan and carry out all sorts of experiments that can turn the tide of the battle.<br></li><li> The Watchers are watching your every move! Earn their favor, and they might just help you out when you’re in a tight spot!</li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>WATCHER</strong> mode:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> A special mode that players enter after being killed.<br></li><li> Bet on your favorite surviving battler.<br></li><li> Influence the battle using anomalies and experiments.</li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "<strong>WATCHERS</strong> is a free-to-play Battle Royale top-down shooter where killed battlers remain in play thanks to the game's unique Watcher game mode. <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1124980/extras/271478a292cf2801daf4ad3dc6302f95.poster.avif?t=1625073737\" width=500 height=374 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1124980/extras/271478a292cf2801daf4ad3dc6302f95.webm?t=1625073737\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1124980/extras/271478a292cf2801daf4ad3dc6302f95.mp4?t=1625073737\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>BATTLER</strong> mode:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> 24-player top-down Battle Royale action.<br></li><li> An unpredictable outcome: the fewer battlers survive, the more Watchers there are to plan and carry out all sorts of experiments that can turn the tide of the battle.<br></li><li> The Watchers are watching your every move! Earn their favor, and they might just help you out when you’re in a tight spot!</li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>WATCHER</strong> mode:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> A special mode that players enter after being killed.<br></li><li> Bet on your favorite surviving battler.<br></li><li> Influence the battle using anomalies and experiments.</li></ul>",
